Fig. 
<number box="[354,366,1270,1294]" pageId="6" pageNumber="175" value="3.0">3</number>
</figureCitation>
G, H). Sternite VIII not distinctly oblong, and posterior margin protruding medially (
<figureCitation box="[1331,1399,1270,1294]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1877,1900]" captionTargetBox="[170,1412,208,1842]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,193,1856]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Medhiama xiaolongmenensis sp. n.: A. male tergite VIII; B. male sternite VIII; C. male tergite X; D. male sternite IX; E. aedeagus, ventral view; F. aedeagus, dorsal view; G. female sternite VIII; H. female genital segment. Scale bars 0.15 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/282241/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="175">
Fig. 
<number box="[1385,1399,1270,1294]" pageId="6" pageNumber="175" value="3.0">3</number>
</figureCitation>
G). Genital segment with pair of subtriangular supplementary sclerites and broad sternite with distinctly protruding anterior margin (
<figureCitation box="[341,407,1339,1363]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1877,1900]" captionTargetBox="[170,1412,208,1842]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,193,1856]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Medhiama xiaolongmenensis sp. n.: A. male tergite VIII; B. male sternite VIII; C. male tergite X; D. male sternite IX; E. aedeagus, ventral view; F. aedeagus, dorsal view; G. female sternite VIII; H. female genital segment. Scale bars 0.15 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/282241/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="175">
Fig. 
<number box="[393,407,1339,1363]" pageId="6" pageNumber="175" value="3.0">3</number>
</figureCitation>
H).
</paragraph>
